quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  50,16,"wlqd khalaqna al'insan, wanaelam ma tuhaddith bih nfsh, wanahn 'aqrab 'iilayh min habl alwarid (whw eirq fi alenq mutasil balqlb)"
  50,17,"hyn yaktub almalakan almtrsdan ean ymynh waean shmalh aemalh. faldhy ean alyamin yaktub alhsnat, waladhi ean alshamal yaktub alsyyat"
  50,18,"ma yalfiz min qawl fytklm bih 'iilaa ladayh malak yrqb qwlh, wyktbh, wahu malak hadr mueadd ldhlk"
  50,19,"wja't shdt almawt wghamrth bialhaqi aldhy laa mrdd lah wala mnas, dhlk ma kunt minh - 'ayuha al'iinsan - tahrub wtrwgh"
  50,20,"wnufkh fi \"alqrn\" nafkhat albaeth althanyt, dhlk alnfkh fi yawm wuque alwaeid aldhy tweead allah bih alkfar"
  50,21,"wja't kulu nafs maeaha malakan, 'ahaduhuma yswqha 'iilaa almhshr, walakhar yashhad ealayha bima eamilat fi aldunya min khayr wshr"
  50,22,"lqd kunt fi ghaflat min hdha aldhy eaynt alyawm 'ayuha al'insan, fakashafna eank ghita'ak aldhy ghtta qlbk, fzalt alghflt enk, fabasaruk alyawm fima tashhad qawiin shdyd"
  50,23,"wqal almalak alkatib alshahid elyh: hdha ma eindi min diwan emlh, wahu ldy mueadd mahfuz hadr"
  50,24,"yaqul allah llmalakyn alssayiq walshhyd baed 'an yafsil bayn alkhlayq: 'alqia fi jahanam kula jahd 'ana allah hu al'ilh alhqqu, kthyr alkufr waltkdhyb meand llhq, mnnae li'ada' ma ealayh min alhuquq fi malh, muetd ealaa eibad allah waealaa hdwdh, shakk fi waedah wweydh, aldhy 'ushrik ballh, febd maeah mebwdana akhar min khlqh, fa'alqiah fi eadhab jahanam alshdyd"
  50,25,"yqwl allah llmalakyn alssayiq walshhyd baed 'an yafsil bayn alkhlayq: 'alqia fi jahanam kula jahd 'ana allah hu al'ilh alhqqu, kthyr alkufr waltkdhyb meand llhq, mnnae li'ada' ma ealayh min alhuquq fi malh, muetd ealaa eibad allah waealaa hdwdh, shakk fi waedah wweydh, aldhy 'ushrik ballh, febd maeah mebwdana akhar min khlqh, fa'alqiah fi eadhab jahanam alshdyd"
  50,26,"yqwl allah llmalakyn alssayiq walshhyd baed 'an yafsil bayn alkhlayq: 'alqia fi jahanam kula jahd 'ana allah hu al'ilh alhqqu, kthyr alkufr waltkdhyb meand llhq, mnnae li'ada' ma ealayh min alhuquq fi malh, muetd ealaa eibad allah waealaa hdwdh, shakk fi waedah wweydh, aldhy 'ushrik ballh, febd maeah mebwdana akhar min khlqh, fa'alqiah fi eadhab jahanam alshdyd"
  50,27,"qal shytanh aldhy kan maeah fi aldnya: rabina ma adllth, wlkn kan fi tariq baeid ean sabil alhda"
  50,28,"qal allah teala: la takhtasimuu ldy alyawm fi mawqif aljaza' walhsab; 'iidh la fayidatan min dhlk, waqad qaddamt 'iilaykum fi aldunya bialwaeid liman kafar bi wesany"
  50,29,"ma yughyar alqawl ldya, walast aedhdhib ahdana bdhnb ahd, fala aedhdhib ahdana 'iilaa bidhanbih baed qiam alhujat elyh"